{"tid":260692,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[老餅, 非主流] 有無人鍾意古典戲曲，包括粵曲/粵劇/京劇/越劇/崑曲...？","createTime":"2017-05-27T20:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T07:05:37.000Z","uid":35221,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a59d0dbacfbeb41eafc3e13026d46ce34abac0e","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T20:20:17.000Z","msg":"繼影視台粵語片post之後<br />\n都發現到有一批老餅係對粵語片有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以忍唔住問埋有無人係對古典戲曲有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有，又鍾意邊套劇或者邊支曲？<br />\n<br />\n戲曲中心即將落成，希望會令粵劇有一番新景象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知各位又有無對古典戲曲特別興趣，無論香港廣東粵劇，以至京劇越劇潮劇崑曲等等唔同類型嘅戲劇都可以交流一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049dab1b9dee1e027d31826c6893bccbad7d305d","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T20:27:17.000Z","msg":"我自己就都係多接觸粵劇，尤其是香港粵劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係忠實任白戲迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最鍾意都係帝女花、紫釵記同牡丹亭驚夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n帝女花之庵遇<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GICDX0Ont9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGICDX0Ont9E&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b3890b51\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GICDX0Ont9E</a><br />\n<br />\n紫釵記之拾釵<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4EVoh1wPooc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4EVoh1wPooc&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=1c32c6db\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4EVoh1wPooc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林家聲一啲武打爲主嘅劇我都覺得好好睇，例如雷鳴金鼓戰笳聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(電影版本)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UGZ9zHUebdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUGZ9zHUebdA&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f337d5ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UGZ9zHUebdA</a><br />\n<br />\n比較新編嘅粵劇，我就鍾意區文鳳，例如吳越春秋(2004)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8AEMFTmSakQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8AEMFTmSakQ&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=94f0dce8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8AEMFTmSakQ</a><br />\n以上呢啲都係老倌擔正，質素有保證<br />\n<br />\n李居明呢幾年新編嗰幾部古典文學改編劇，其實都唔錯，好似蝶海情僧，最不知所謂就係無啦啦整套毛澤東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。(個人認為李居明雖然好鍾意張揚，又自戀，成日大大隻字放大自己個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係無可否認而家粵劇真係要有人搞起佢，否則無以為繼)"},{"pid":"c062b105996faef140c2a8eb0400ed8cdee2b797","tid":260692,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T20:30:36.000Z","msg":"睇過下粵劇發展史<br />\n覺得唐滌生好神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91ce9428b7efb00f0fa93d897a1b0ee1b40bad9","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T20:33:51.000Z","msg":"粵曲嚟講我特別鍾意聽南音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白駒榮(仙姐伯爺)唱客途秋恨真係聽出耳油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Kuu2RjRR0bg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKuu2RjRR0bg&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=cab12680\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Kuu2RjRR0bg</a><br />\n<br />\n何非凡碧海狂僧則係好有趣嘅一支曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Psyemp91hwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPsyemp91hwg&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=910cce74\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Psyemp91hwg</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，小明星嘅風流夢、夜半歌聲都幾適合夜闌人靜欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜半歌聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Rn4qMUFaCgY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRn4qMUFaCgY&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=3c247aa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Rn4qMUFaCgY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟始終都唔係粵劇界一分子，只不過係一介觀眾，不過真係好希望有多啲人留意下戲曲，保護呢啲珍貴文化，盡量都係出下post交流下意見，所以都希望有人推下post，留意下都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a703d82870bfd310ce60bcd1028662a2c2d7873","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T20:37:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇過下粵劇發展史<br />\n覺得唐滌生好神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唐公實在係一代宗師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢編劇生涯得二十年，已經寫咗400幾部粵劇，真係粵劇界神人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係平心而論，佢咁多產，難免有次貨，有啲其實都係粗製濫造<br />\n不過佢的確將香港粵劇推到去藝術殿堂層面，呢個無庸質疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c227a20921117b49c69f70747dcd79e8cc1fc48a","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T22:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecae78faa1091b16725a6584a24f628ea66d5277","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T00:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7864ea2210ecc2ec018e9cf3cc8da3c19b53c8c4","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1140dac64350f11a29f472455ccd0281ca06b327","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T10:11:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa517544b7a7c9db0a8ca596a724488fe06d01c","tid":260692,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"無乜興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f98fe2f92bcd7354b9d3e3a6fbde13cadc338ba","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無乜興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d6d64ba519744e62e3ca79b28c1d7577174216","tid":260692,"uid":78501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"af390a4628edf3fb729682075222f42850fb820b","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T19:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a0736f515ba4bdd3daac274c507888a0ec58b7","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T02:35:59.000Z","msg":"有無人鍾意任芳戲寶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6920f2123178975059c4e5cd1d2742642943f430","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi