e><br />\n正呀，我都好鍾意牡丹亭驚夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有咩研究心得/發現？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd120bec8fa693cff45360fe45fa2d9cb2b7a1f4","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解咁夜仲唔瞓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得閒tg me 傾  cy0451</blockquote><br />\n其實係點學法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38d46739029e2b69a3fa0eff070c54bd8831516","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T17:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a62e88fd3e66ad6eaa18a63a7e8dfff5481f0b4","tid":260692,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T13:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}